{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTags:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSDictionary","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSDictionary"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"tags"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"tags","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Dictionary of tag names and values to set for the current device"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags are key-value pairs that enable targeted push notifications based on user attributes"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and behavior. Use tags to segment your audience and send personalized messages to specific"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"user groups."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Supported Tag Types","anchor":"Supported-Tag-Types"},{"header":"row","type":"table","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Type"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Example"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Description","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"String"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"\"city\": \"New York\"","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Text values","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Integer"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"age\": 25"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Numeric values","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Boolean","type":"text"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"\"isPremium\": true","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"True\/false values","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"List"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"interests\": [\"sports\", \"music\"]"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Arrays of strings"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Date"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"\"lastPurchase\": Date()","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"NSDate objects"}],"type":"paragraph"}]]]},{"text":"Example","level":2,"anchor":"Example","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Update user profile tags after account changes:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class UserProfileManager {","","    func updateUserTags(for user: User) {","        var tags: [String: Any] = [","            \"user_id\": user.id,","            \"email_verified\": user.isEmailVerified,","            \"account_type\": user.accountType.rawValue,","            \"signup_date\": user.createdAt,","            \"app_version\": Bundle.main.appVersion","        ]","","        \/\/ Add subscription info if premium","        if let subscription = user.subscription {","            tags[\"subscription_tier\"] = subscription.tier.rawValue","            tags[\"subscription_expiry\"] = subscription.expiryDate","            tags[\"is_premium\"] = true","        } else {","            tags[\"is_premium\"] = false","        }","","        \/\/ Add user preferences","        if !user.interests.isEmpty {","            tags[\"interests\"] = user.interests","        }","","        \/\/ Add location if available","        if let location = user.location {","            tags[\"country\"] = location.country","            tags[\"city\"] = location.city","            tags[\"timezone\"] = location.timezone","        }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags(tags)","        Logger.debug(\"User tags updated: \\(tags.keys.joined(separator: \", \"))\")","    }","","    func trackPurchase(product: Product, amount: Decimal) {","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"last_purchase_date\": Date(),","            \"last_purchase_amount\": NSDecimalNumber(decimal: amount),","            \"last_purchase_category\": product.category,","            \"total_purchases\": incrementTag(\"total_purchases\")","        ])","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setTags:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Sets user tags for device segmentation.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/settags:"]}],"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setTags:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTags:"}],"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setTags:","title":"setTags:","roleHeading":"Type Method","role":"symbol"},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"PWConfiguration"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setTags:":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setTags:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setTags:","title":"setTags:","abstract":[{"text":"Sets user tags for device segmentation.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTags:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/settags:"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","type":"topic"}}}